<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَيُؤَيِّدُهُ قَوْلُهُ بَعْدَهُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَصَاحِ تَرَى بَرْقًا أُرِيكَ وَمِيضَهُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ الْفَرَزْدَقِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَشِيَّةَ سَالَ الْمِرْبَدَانِ كِلَاهُمَا ... سَحَابَةَ مَوْتٍ بِالسُّيُوفِ الصَّوَارِمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَإِنَّمَا هُوَ مِرْبَدُ الْبَصْرَةِ فَقَطْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c1">"وَدَارٍ لَهَا بِالرَّقْمَتَيْنِ"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c1">"بِبَطْنِ الْمَكَّتَيْنِ"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُ جَرِيرٍ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لَمَّا مَرَرْتُ بِالدَّيْرَيْنِ أَرَّقَنِي ... صَوْتُ الدَّجَاجِ وَقَرْعٌ بِالنَّوَاقِيسِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قَالُوا:</span> أَرَادَ <span class="c1">"دَيْرَ الْوَلِيدِ"</span> فَثَنَّاهُ بِاعْتِبَارِ مَا حَوْلَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>الْقِسْمُ الثَّانِي عَشَرَ. إِطْلَاقُ الْجَمْعِ وَإِرَادَةُ الْوَاحِدِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">كَقَوْلِهِ:</span> <span class="c3">{يا أيها الرسل كلوا من الطيبات}</span> إِلَى قَوْلِهِ: {فَذَرْهُمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>